subject: Thank you for your mail.
body:
Thank you for your mail. 
Attention please beneficiary
 We're needed your urgent response back with a gift card $50 dollars to make the delivery fee?

subject: Re:   Thank you for your mail.
body:
Hello there! Thank you for reaching out to me. I appreciate your message. Could you please provide me with more details about the delivery fee and how it is related to the gift card dollars? I want to make sure I understand everything clearly before proceeding.

Best wishes,
Muriel
